dataIdInfo.idAbs: This line data layer represents roads for Trempealeau County, Wisconsin in 2017. It is a feature class within the geodatabase, Trempealeau_Roads_2017.gdb.[Road centerlines for Trempealeau County, Wisconsin. Attributes are based on NENA standards and are MSAG valid where applicable.]
dataIdInfo.idPurp: This layer is intended for reference and mapping purposes, and may be used for basic applications such as viewing, querying, and map output production, or to provide a basemap to support graphical overlays and analysis with other spatial data. [This data was created specially for use in an emergency dispatch mapping software. Data is also used for general purpose mapping for such data layers as Parcels and roads.]
